data.description: Looking for a blend of comfort, convenience, and serenity? This fully updated 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath bi-level home has it all. It offers a well-maintained and stylish environment. Whether you're seeking a spacious master suite, a modern kitchen, updated bathrooms, a family room, or modern amenities, this home has you covered. It features a new septic tank. All appliances, including a BRAND NEW stove, dishwasher, and washer and dryer, will remain in the home. A private backyard and a 2-car garage complete this wonderful place to call home!
